description: Discover how to make banana bread with this classic recipe that uses simple ingredients you probably already have in your house. Plus, the browner the bananas the better. There's no beating - just mixing - this no-fuss favourite.
name: Easy Banana Bread Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Transfer mixture to prepared pan and bake for 1 hour or until a skewer inserted into centre comes out clean. Stand bread in pan for 10 minutes before transferring to a wire rack to cool. Slice and serve.
